				<td colspan="2"><span>Kunark mobs work different on ranged aggro don't they? They &quot;forget&quot; about you temporarily and will not give chase when out of the certain range. I know for a fact that it's different in PoP but in Kunark I'm 90% sure that's the case, I remember reading about it here and experiencing it in DL and KC. 
<br />
Try messing around in Seb with aggro ranges, grab a frog or two then hoof it way out of range and see if they still come knocking, if they do then I'm wrong, if they don't then it's just a range issue. 
